	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Mar 10th 10:32 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.10]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>It never fails to amuse me when someone comes on a board saying that their race is the best race for a particular class.&nbsp;&nbsp;Please, if you do believe this keep that little secret to yourself so no one else knows will know this.  Verant didn't make one race best for a certain class, but gave us many different choices that would allow us to play classes different.  Yes, yes, I know your orge and other troll SK's can deal out a good deal of damage, but to say that they are the best race is just such a stupid comment to say.  A DE with a INT of 150+ would be able to woop most people let alone a dimwitted orge/troll.  I have nothing against either of these two races, but it just angers me to no end when someone comes in here on a subject that has been debated over and over without any type of resolution.  Just think how boring things would get if there where best races for a class, even though there are some races much better suited for a class.  We would be seeing the same thing everywhere, Barbarian-warriors(cant stand seeing these guys everywhere), are an example of a class-race that's been so overused.  So please, if you need to tell someone that you amazingly found the best race for SK's, by all means tell someone, just not here.  I think more than a few of us are sick of this topic.<br><br>Sorry for the venting, well not too sorry.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
